<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8281380>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitat, habit and morphology of Corydalis mianxianensis (D. Wang et al. 210003). A. habitat; B. inflorescence; C. fruits; D–G. flower showing the lateral view (D), front view (E), adaxial view of flower showing the apex of upper petal (F) and abaxial view of flower showing the apex of lower petal (G)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8281380/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8281382>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Corydalis mianxianensis (a–m) (D. Wang et al. 210003). a. bracts; b. flower with bract; c. sepals; d. upper petals; e. lower petals; f. spur and nectary; g. inner petals; h. stamens; i. pistil with attached sepals and bract and pedicel; j. stigmas showing variation among individuals; k. fruits; l. seeds; and m. dissected floral parts that are illustrated to the same scale bar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8281382/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

